{"TopicId":95993,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Slight freeze every 5 seconds (or so)","CreatedByName":"SessoSaidSo","CreatedById":111600,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-08T04:38:35Z","PageNum":10,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Babich","CreatedById":185337,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-21T07:25:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223252044\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002295993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221514144543\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156173\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CanOmer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 25.12.2017 at 12:42 AM, CanOmer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have same problem. Is there any solution?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/139128-112-memgraph-1000/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ethis \u003C/a\u003Emod or turn off antialiasing in settings\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-02-21T07:25:16Z\u0022 title=\u002202/21/2018 07:25  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 21, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Babich\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ss8913","CreatedById":94747,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-08T03:15:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have tried memgraph, turning off AA, setting max prerendered frames to 1 in the nvidia control panel... DirectX, OpenGL... everything everyone on every forum I can find, has suggested, and this is still happening.\u00A0 Seems to sometimes not happen, sometimes only a little, sometimes *a lot*.. cannot figure out what\u0027s affecting the rate, but.. if anyone has any suggestions other than what I just mentinoed..\u00A0please let me know \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nNote - only happens in flight to me, not in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-08T03:18:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223373598\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002295993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525749301\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002294747\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ss8913\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, ss8913 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have tried memgraph, turning off AA, setting max prerendered frames to 1 in the nvidia control panel... DirectX, OpenGL... everything everyone on every forum I can find, has suggested, and this is still happening.\u00A0 Seems to sometimes not happen, sometimes only a little, sometimes *a lot*.. cannot figure out what\u0027s affecting the rate, but.. if anyone has any suggestions other than what I just mentinoed..\u00A0please let me know \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nNote - only happens in flight to me, not in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow much memory do you have on the machine? My best guess is a GC issue. I wold recommend MemGraph or GCMonitor to give a peek in what KSP and the mods are doing with the memory.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ss8913","CreatedById":94747,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-08T05:38:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a brand new pc.. i7 8700K, 1080ti with 11gb vram, 32gb ddr4 main memory, and ksp is installed on a Samsung evo ssd.. I was hoping the new rig would fix the problem. But no.\u00A0 Framerates and such are of course much faster than the old box, but the stutter persists.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-08T05:56:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s hard to believe, but sometimes putting more RAM into the problem makes it worse.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith more RAM to use, the GC usually is encouraged to \u0022waste\u0022 more RAM before collecting the garbage - and when finally it does it, there\u0027re so much trash that it halts for far more time than before. Kind of \u0022better halts 0.5sec each 2 secs than 4 secs each 10\u0022 issue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut I\u0027m just guessing. You need a run monitoring the heap using something like GCMonitor to be sure about what\u0027s happening.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt can be something inside Unity, for example.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dafni","CreatedById":149636,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-08T06:57:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223373638\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002295993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525757885\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002294747\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ss8913\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, ss8913 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a brand new pc.. i7 8700K, 1080ti with 11gb vram, 32gb ddr4 main memory, and ksp is installed on a Samsung evo ssd.. I was hoping the new rig would fix the problem. But no.\u00A0 Framerates and such are of course much faster than the old box, but the stutter persists.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMan, I hope you can fix this. Please keep us updated.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Casper_83","CreatedById":179115,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-05T20:33:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is still a problem, I hoped they would fix this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Fix freeze problem\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Steam modsupport\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. include \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E and IR in the game!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dxeh","CreatedById":186391,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-26T09:57:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223481828\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002295993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221541449990\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179115\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Casper_83\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/5/2018 at 9:33 PM, Casper_83 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is still a problem, I hoped they would fix this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Fix freeze problem\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Steam modsupport\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. include \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E and IR in the game!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIll go for nr. 3!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starlord Kerman","CreatedById":177240,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-20T07:25:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve just started having this problem where it briefly (but noticeably and annoyingly) pauses every 3-4 seconds, even in the Spaceplane Hanger. I have run KSP with the task manager open and it doesn\u0027t go above 50% memory usage and is even less on the CPU and GPU. I have also tried forcing it to use opengl which didn\u0027t help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheEeveeLovers","CreatedById":192384,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T18:52:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00221705830\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002295993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221423353385\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MircoMars\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/7/2015 at 6:56 PM, MircoMars said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nit also helps if you assign KSP to one CPU core only and try to get everything else off that core.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey removed the core affinity from windows 10 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheEeveeLovers","CreatedById":192384,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T19:05:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223511361\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002295993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221545818252\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022186391\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022dxeh\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 12/26/2018 at 4:57 AM, dxeh said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIll go for nr. 3!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223481828\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002295993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221541449990\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179115\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Casper_83\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/5/2018 at 3:33 PM, Casper_83 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is still a problem, I hoped they would fix this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Fix freeze problem\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Steam modsupport\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. include \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E and IR in the game!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey added IR into breaking ground\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Drinarii","CreatedById":198897,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T19:53:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223637556\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002295993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221563563121\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192384\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheEeveeLovers\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n46 minutes ago, TheEeveeLovers said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey added IR into breaking ground\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow did they really add IR into breaking ground or are you joking?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Casper_83","CreatedById":179115,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-22T08:11:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223637556\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002295993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221563563121\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192384\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheEeveeLovers\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/19/2019 at 9:05 PM, TheEeveeLovers said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey added IR into breaking ground\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFinally 1/3 of 3 fixed I have not tried it yet, but maybe 1. is fixed also \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223637591\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002295993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221563566006\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022198897\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Drinarii\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/19/2019 at 9:53 PM, Drinarii said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow did they really add IR into breaking ground or are you joking?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot really, they made their own, Still amazing, but missing a gantry type for making cranes in my opinion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"szundi","CreatedById":200607,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-04T18:22:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCaptain here. You may have too much RAM, Unity allocates too much, so it has to do big GCs. I decreased the problem until it became quite usable by creating a RAM disk, leaving just enough RAM (based on guess and experiencing) for Kerbal Space Program to run smoothly without swapping. This made GCs smaller, more frequent and faster. It is not perfect, but much better. Cheers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}